Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:40.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:46.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:52.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:58.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:04.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:10.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:16.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:20.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:28.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:35.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:35.02,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當邪惡在此世蔓延之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會現身的希望之戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著星座之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發蘊藏在身體中的能量「小宇宙」進行著戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是 保護大地上愛與和平的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士光牙尋找雅典娜的旅程還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同逃出Palaestra的海蛇座市會合後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的聖鬥士們來到了土之遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時 市突然化身為水蛇座白銀聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:02:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為瑪爾斯的手下對光牙等人發動了進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗找到了白銀聖鬥士米開朗基羅的藏身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞了核心 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了土之小宇宙水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而面對為了尊嚴而誤入歧途的市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳再度爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙雖然很惦念市今後的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是繼續向下一個遺跡進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們 燃起內心的小宇宙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在命運的星辰之下！聖鬥士們的生存之路！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長途跋涉 又破壞了兩個核心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很耗費精力和體力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起之前居住的島了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個遺跡 在海的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是火星士！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已確認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再交給白銀聖鬥士了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們火星士追擊部隊螞蟻分隊來打敗你們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打敗這些蟻類火星士 強行突破嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 必須要先考慮阿莉雅的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了 準備進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉…拉辛斯基隊長 這該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我追！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉目標！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他們跑了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來順利擺脫他們了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 趁現在快去港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人和車的密度是什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是光牙第一次來大都市呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒 居然有這樣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多遊客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說世界各地的風景名勝以及自然資源豐富的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是湖泊乾涸就是花田枯萎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 遊客才會在這裡集中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.34,0:05:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是因為巴比倫塔的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用為此多慮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是這艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正要啟航了 真走運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有十分鐘就要發船了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘客請在這裡買票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡付錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船就要開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生給的錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像丟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦 這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 上不了船也就無法繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想個法子才行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船的話 還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以乘我的小艇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你倒是小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打碎的盤子錢 可是要從你的工錢裡扣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我家開的食宿公寓（pension）Paulo&Anne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食宿公寓是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是提供住宿的地方       
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是一種給人居家感的賓館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 老太婆 我剛帶回來幾個打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎…就這麼幾個小毛頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞出什麼岔子我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一直都是我和老太婆兩個人忙活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近客人實在太多 忙得不可開交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想讓你們來幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士可以打工嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會得到諒解的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是為了拯救雅典娜而打的工啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好工作 我會給你們出船的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 美麗的女士們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店將為您提供上等美味佳餚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都要手洗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鉚足幹勁上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這掃除做得跟雜耍似的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您點了咖啡歐蕾 檸檬茶 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及巧克力蛋糕兩塊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我們沒點蛋糕啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我送給二位的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 點菜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 二位美女是從哪兒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 又手滑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你到底要打碎多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不好好幹 就給我滾蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅就不用了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子洗起盤子來才更得心應手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你好久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服務生只有我一個 力有不逮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你力有不逮！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直在和女孩子聊天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 實在是太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是剛來的新人 還沒適應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝高了就早點回家睡覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗了半天還沒完…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這也是為了能前往下一個遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鷹座聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力過大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 有飛賊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們別幹了 究竟是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然難以啟齒 不過有你們在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而增加我們的工作量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要炒我們魷魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我們一次機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會用拿手的技法來取悅觀眾的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿手的技法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位女士們 先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Paulo&Anne特別火焰料理秀開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩特製
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷刷地加上調味料 請品嚐吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺人嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子 那是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到全體被炒魷魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這下借船的事情還辦的成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了給我們坐船作為打工的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都被解雇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們幫忙 店裡反而更忙亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也不太方便開船出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 如何才能過海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人倒是輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明因為瑪爾斯的關係 整個世界已經陷入危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不知道瑪爾斯的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說瑪爾斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家連聖鬥士的存在都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不為人知呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我住在小島上的時候 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經聽沙織小姐這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得接受聖鬥士的訓練不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人 都是沿著星辰所定的命運生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如有人是在幸福的星辰庇護下出生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人則生在不幸的星辰下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有各自有各種各樣的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你是在聖鬥士的星辰下出生的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如沙織小姐所說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我是在聖鬥士的星辰庇護下出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗你們也一定都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上跟我們年紀差不多的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都享受著普通的青春 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開朗快樂的生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的人生 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能痛苦又嚴苛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我們要在聖鬥士的星辰下 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是段感人肺腑的話啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是命中注定要在這裡死去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你們再逃個看看？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會把這座城裡的人全部殺掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要開始什麼表演嗎？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量不要波及旁人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.10,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻分隊 攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危 危險 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就說過　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的命運就是葬身於此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要死在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們是在聖鬥士之星辰的指引下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼盡全力生活的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區…區區聖鬥士 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想贏過火星士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他們見識一下我們的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄行進 Hell's Proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈焰暴徒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士流忍法 龜甲斬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬閃光拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真棒　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場精彩的演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很受感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…演出是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是扣人心弦吶 著實讓人大吃一驚勒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你們幾個竟然是旅行藝人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到竟然能讓旅客這麼高興　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個再回來我的店裡打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…都說了這不是演出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場天大的誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下也給你們的旅店痛快地宣傳了一把呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭子 如果客人繼續增加我們該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這次的報酬我們就不客氣嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小店可是隨時恭候的喲　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可一定要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.97,0:21:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 你們店一定要變成一個能吸引更多可愛妹子的旅店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我們總算能坐上船了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.58,0:21:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 總覺得今天過得好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向火之遺跡進發的道路儘是溪谷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙一行一邊躲避敵人一邊前行 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一位獨行的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位少女懂得修復損傷聖衣的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是地獄犬座Cerberus的多萊卻攻了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應守護之物！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖衣修復師與傳說中的礦石！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受過小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
